  <div class="row" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
    <div class="span7">
      <h4>Meet your fellow New Yorkers</h4>
      <p>Ever wanted to connect with the millions of New Yorkers walking past you? Each day brings opportunities to make new friends and share experiences. All too often, we can forget to notice the people around us. Nametag Day aims to break this barrier and strengthen the human element of the New York experience, adding a bit of spontaneity and silliness to people's day.
      </p>

    </div>
    <div class="span5">
